18:26.605 --> 18:29.165
Yes, it was a factor.

18:45.424 --> 18:47.756
- Alan.
- Shirley.

18:47.860 --> 18:50.385
- How are we doing?
- If you mean with Denny...

18:50.496 --> 18:52.828
