of Sydney going down.

23:52.731 --> 23:54.665
I- I never thought I'd say this...

23:54.766 --> 23:58.827
but I can't bring myself
to so much as look at a gun.

24:00.138 --> 24:02.163
- Denny.
- The way he fell...

24:02.274 --> 24:04.469
