24:10.615 --> 24:13.209
Alan, so help me God...

24:13.318 --> 24:17.721
if you ever catch me looking
at a gun again-

24:44.249 --> 24:45.910
How we doing?

24:49.955 --> 24:53.152
- A list of everything you love about me.
- That's my closing.

24:53.258 --> 24:57.194
What do I say?
The police can legally require an I. D.

24:57.295 --> 24:59.195
He resisted arrest.

24:59.297 --> 25:02.027
Under the law, he's guilty.

25:02.133 --> 25:06.593
What am I supposed to do?
Ask that the jury disregard the law?

25:07.772 --> 25:09.740
You need to have faith
in them, Chelina.

25:09.841 --> 25:13.641
You need to remember these are people
of conscience, of compassion.

25:13.745 --> 25:16.509
