they're too stupid to get off jury duty.

25:16.615 --> 25:19.243
I am not that cynical.

25:19.351 --> 25:21.182
I know you're not.

25:23.188 --> 25:25.281
Shirley Schmidt.

25:29.127 --> 25:31.925
She assigned me to a case
recently to close.

25:32.030 --> 25:37.798
She felt I had a certain capacity
to see the darkness in people's hearts.

25:39.004 --> 25:42.405
One of the reasons
I wanted you on this case...

25:42.507 --> 25:45.499
among other reasons...

25:45.610 --> 25:51.310
I think you have a capacity to tap into
what is fundamentally decent about people.

25:52.918 --> 25:58.049
I believe if you call on this jury
to do what is right...

25:58.156 --> 26:01.091
morally right, if not legally...

26:05.230 --> 26:07.198
they will follow.

26:20.879 --> 26:23.746
So, what pointers
do you have specifically?

26:23.848 --> 26:26.112
- I have another date.
- Same girl?

26:26.217 --> 26:28.651
