- I'll take over from here.

33:50.628 --> 33:53.062
Don't you dare.

33:53.164 --> 33:55.428
- And don't shoot anybody.
- Oh, please.

33:59.337 --> 34:01.965
- Did they arrest Denny again?
- Apparently not.

34:02.073 --> 34:05.008
- It appears he saved everyone.
- What about the underlying charges?

34:05.109 --> 34:07.577
As far as I know, they still stand.

34:11.282 --> 34:15.116
- Um, we need to talk.
- We most certainly do.

34:15.219 --> 34:17.414
It was a kissing demonstration.

34:19.590 --> 34:23.047
- We had sex.
- I'm aware of that.

34:25.362 --> 34:27.956
- On the floor.
